    "The initial step in implementing the feature-grained preference analysis outlined in Sect. 3.1 is to collect datasets of product design features.",
    "The dataset includes appearance design parameters, feature design parameters, functional design parameters, and the user satisfaction label.",
    "The collected features may have missing values, but these features cannot be abandoned directly.",
    "In addition, most algorithms can handle only numerical data, so it is necessary to encode text features and convert them to numerical variables.",
    "Figure 6 shows the feature preprocessing procedure."
